    "sketchCode": "int potPin = A0;\nint ledPin = 9;\nint potValue = 0;\nint brightness = 255;\n\nvoid setup() {\n  pinMode(ledPin, OUTPUT);\n  pinMode(14, INPUT);\n  Serial.begin(9600);\n}\n\nvoid loop() {\n  potValue = analogRead(potPin);\n  Serial.print(potValue);\n  brightness = map(potValue, 0, 1023, 0, 255);\n  analogWrite(ledPin, brightness);\n  delay(10);\n}\n\n",
